mongoose 
is an object Data Modeling (ODM) library for mongoDB and node.js .it manages relationship b/w data provides schema validation and is used to translate between objects in code and the representation of those object in MongoDb

or

Mongoose is an Object Document Mapper (ODM) library for MongoDB and Node.js.  that make using MongoDB easier by translating documnt in a mongodb data base to object in the program


node


mongoose.connect(here we can give path where is my database)
mongoose.connect("mongodb://localhost27017/ttchanell",{userNewUrlParse:true,useUnifiedT0pology:true })
